    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This unit is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical integrity is prioritized with a recently serviced dual-VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to maintain structural rigidity under high torque loads. The chassis features a factory-spec limited-slip differential and M-tuned suspension geometry for optimal turn-in and corner-exit traction. Presented in honest 'good' condition, this M3 offers a pure analog driving experience with a well-maintained drivetrain and a sonorous exhaust note.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
