    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and is totally ready to hit the road with a new owner! Whether you're zipping around town for errands or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car handles beautifully and has been very well-maintained. It\u2019s super dependable and just looking for its next adventure\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
