    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, a hallmark of naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS timing for exceptional throttle response. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-Differential Lock, ensuring predictable torque bias during spirited cornering. This example remains structurally robust with documented subframe inspection and recent preventative maintenance on the rod bearings and cooling system. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the tactile feedback only a well-sorted E46 can provide. While the aesthetics reflect its status as a driven machine, its mechanical integrity makes it a premier candidate for the discerning purist.",
